r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.breckenridge.com/info/summer.aspx">http://www.breckenridge.com/info/summer.aspx</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=breckenridge,+co&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876af63d6c26e7c1:0x628d8f7f6680a27a,Breckenridge,+CO&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XrgYTsqmBJGFsALRztTCBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CCsQ8gEwAA"><strong>Lake Dillon</strong></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.townofdillon.com/">http://www.townofdillon.com/</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Shopping</strong>:\r\n\r\n<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">Park Meadows Mall</a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">The Streets at Southglenn</a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">The 16<sup>th</sup> Street Mall</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Biking</strong>:\r\n\r\nThere are bikes available to rent (<a href="http://denver.bcycle.com/">http://denver.bcycle.com/</a>) all over downtown, and trails along the Platt River and Cherry Creek\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Dining</strong>:\r\n\r\nGo to <a href="http://www.Opentable.com">Opentable.com</a> to find great places to eat, and to make a reservation!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Wedding Day Itinerary:</strong></p>\r\nThe wedding will be at Hudson Gardens in Littleton, CO\r\n\r\n<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=6115+South+Santa+Fe+Drive&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c81d044459e75:0x577994b826cbc441,6115+S+Santa+Fe+Dr,+Littleton,+CO+80120&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=oJcYTun0KOOmsAKbkaHCBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CCEQ8gEwAA">6115 South Santa Fe Drive</a>\r\n\r\nCeremony: 11am at Monet’s Place\r\n\r\nBrunch Reception immediately following in the Welcome Garden until 2:30pm\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Things to do while in Denver', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '37-revision-9', '', '', '2011-07-09 20:29:42', '2011-07-09 20:29:42', '', 37, 'http://wedding.lecocq.us/2011/07/37-revision-9/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(49, 2, '2011-07-11 18:46:11', '2011-07-11 18:46:11', '<div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Welcome to Denver!</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>And to Dan and Erin’s Wedding!</strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Thank you so much for coming to share this day with us!</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nLooking for things to do in Denver before or after the wedding?\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Denver Zoo</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2300+Steele+St+Denver&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c7951c97c8cbf:0xac8baa231a1f330,2300+Steele+St,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=RJQYTpOGIIaKsQKp4O3BBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBkQ8gEwAA">2300 Steele St</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.denverzoo.org">www.denverzoo.org</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Denver Museum of Nature and Science</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">2001 Colorado Blvd</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.dmns.org">www.dmns.org</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Denver Downtown Aquarium</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">700 Water Street</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.aquariumrestaurants.com/downtownaquariumdenver/">http://www.aquariumrestaurants.com/downtownaquariumdenver/</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Waterworld Water Park</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">1800 E. 89<sup>th</sup> Ave (88<sup>th</sup> and Pecos)</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.waterworldcolorado.com/">http://www.waterworldcolorado.com/\r\n</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Elitch Gardens Amusement Park</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">2000 Elitch Circle (I-25 and Speer Blvd)</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.elitchgardens.com  ">www.elitchgardens.com</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Denver Botanic Gardens</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">1007 York St</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.botanicgardens.org">www.botanicgardens.org</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>The Molly Brown House and Museum</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">1340 Pennsylvania St</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.mollybrown.org">www.mollybrown.org</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Denver Art Museum</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">100 West 14th Avenue Parkway</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.denverartmuseum.org">www.denverartmuseum.org</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Coors Brewery</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">13<sup>th</sup> and Ford st (Golden)</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.millercoors.com">www.millercoors.com</a>\r\n\r\nDaily Tours 10-4\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Coors Field (Home of Rockies Baseball)</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">2001 Blake Street</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.coloradorockies.com">www.coloradorockies.com</a>\r\n\r\nTours Mon-Sat 10, 12, and 2 (no 2pm tour on game days)\r\n\r\nGames: Sat: vs Brewers 6:10 pm\r\n\r\nSun: vs Brewers 1:10 pm\r\n\r\nMon: vs Braves 6:10 pm\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">Invesco Field at Mile High (Home of the Broncos)</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.coloradosports.org">www.coloradosports.org</a>\r\n\r\nTours Tues-Sat 10am-2pm\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Venice on the Creek (Gondola Ride down Cherry Creek)</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">Larimer and Speer Blvd</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.veniceonthecreek.com">www.veniceonthecreek.com</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>For the Outdoors-y:</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?hl=en&amp;q=lookout+mountain,+colorado&amp;bav=on.2,or.r_gc.r_pw.&amp;biw=1276&amp;bih=682&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876b9b6184e03ecb:0x56651138d1d1942c,Lookout+Mountain,+Golden,+CO&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=ubMYTuj4HOOKsQLCuazCBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=2&amp;ved=0CCkQ8gEwAQ">Lookout Mountain</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://jeffco.us/openspace/openspace_T56_R14.htm">http://jeffco.us/openspace/openspace_T56_R14.htm</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://denver.about.com/od/sportsrecreation/tp/hikes.htm">http://denver.about.com/od/sportsrecreation/tp/hikes.htm</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=keystone,+co&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876a5724e77c6583:0x43670c887d2ffa61,Keystone,+CO&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=1bcYTs7EG9T_sQLrnMHCBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=3&amp;ved=0CHAQ8gEwAg">Keystone</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.keystoneresort.com/activities/mountain-biking.aspx">http://www.keystoneresort.com/activities/mountain-biking.aspx</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=breckenridge,+co&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876af63d6c26e7c1:0x628d8f7f6680a27a,Breckenridge,+CO&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XrgYTsqmBJGFsALRztTCBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CCsQ8gEwAA">Summer in Brekenridge</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.breckenridge.com/info/summer.aspx">http://www.breckenridge.com/info/summer.aspx</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=breckenridge,+co&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876af63d6c26e7c1:0x628d8f7f6680a27a,Breckenridge,+CO&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XrgYTsqmBJGFsALRztTCBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CCsQ8gEwAA"><strong>Lake Dillon</strong></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.townofdillon.com/">http://www.townofdillon.com/</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Shopping</strong>:\r\n\r\n<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">Park Meadows Mall</a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.shopsouthglenn.com/">The Streets at Southglenn</a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=2001+Colorado+Blvd&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c79544a568923:0x5c615a3eb6fb234f,2001+Colorado+Blvd,+Denver,+CO+80205&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=XZQYToyMKOOHsgLQ3vHBBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBUQ8gEwAA">The 16<sup>th</sup> Street Mall</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Biking</strong>:\r\n\r\nThere are bikes available to rent (<a href="http://denver.bcycle.com/">http://denver.bcycle.com/</a>) all over downtown, and trails along the Platt River and Cherry Creek\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Dining</strong>:\r\n\r\nGo to <a href="http://www.Opentable.com">Opentable.com</a> to find great places to eat, and to make a reservation!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Wedding Day Itinerary:</strong></p>\r\nThe wedding will be at Hudson Gardens in Littleton, CO\r\n\r\n<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?q=6115+South+Santa+Fe+Drive&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x876c81d044459e75:0x577994b826cbc441,6115+S+Santa+Fe+Dr,+Littleton,+CO+80120&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=oJcYTun0KOOmsAKbkaHCBw&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=geocode_result&amp;ct=title&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CCEQ8gEwAA">6115 South Santa Fe Drive</a>\r\n\r\nCeremony: 11am at Monet’s Place\r\n\r\nBrunch Reception immediately following in the Welcome Garden until 2:30pm\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Things to do while in Denver', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '37-revision-11', '', '', '2011-07-11 18:46:11', '2011-07-11 18:46:11', '', 37, 'http://wedding.lecocq.us/2011/07/37-revision-11/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
